类 TemporalAccessorParser

    public final class TemporalAccessorParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements Parser<java.time.temporal.TemporalAccessor>
    Parser implementation for a JSR-310 TemporalAccessor, using a DateTimeFormatter) (the contextual one, if available).
    从以下版本开始:
    4.0
    作者:
    Juergen Hoeller
